{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "贝尔扎克 第3话 不断寻求强敌的原因",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这家伙……\\n好难缠啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呜……各位，撤退吧！\\n先退回城里！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "知道了。撤退吧……\\n贝尔扎克，你听到了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "怎么，只有这种程度吗！\\n让我更享受一点啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "贝尔扎克！快撤退！\\n离开那头魔兽！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "贝尔扎克，\\n要撤退了，快点。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "不要妨碍我！\\n我要继续战斗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃……作战计划变更！\\n所有人，一起掩护贝尔扎克！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "在这里消灭那头魔兽！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "贝尔扎克，\\n请让我看看你的伤势。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "最后一个治疗我就行。\\n优先其他人吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你的伤势是最重的，\\n因为你太胡来了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "是吗……\\n给你添麻烦了，真是抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "真是的……算了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "来吧，请让我看看伤势。\\n我马上给你治疗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "贝尔扎克，现在有空吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "嗯……是今天战斗的事吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "给大家添了麻烦，\\n实在抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "真是吓出我一身冷汗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你为什么……\\n会那么执着于和强敌战斗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "自我懂事起，我的人生\\n就充斥着无尽的战斗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "不战斗就会被杀死。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "在那种环境下，\\n日复一日地战斗、胜利、存活……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "等我注意到的时候，\\n自己已经变得异常了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是，怎么回事……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "只有在和强敌战斗的过程中，\\n我才能体会到活着的实感。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "所以我才不断寻求与强者战斗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "就算在战斗中死去，\\n我也不后悔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "如果因为这一点，\\n让你和大家觉得困扰……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110050_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝尔扎克",
            "context": "我就……离开这座城堡吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "之前说想和龙战斗，\\n也是因为这个吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我不能让他那样战斗。\\n又不想让他就这么离开……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样一来……\\n我只有一个办法！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}